/* GCTools - A PHP Framework			*/
/* Developed by: J. "Giga" Murphy		*/
/*		and M. "Beanyhead" Parker	*/
/* Website: http://www.gigacreations.net/	*/
/************************************************/

GCTools is a PHP framework that is meant to enable developers to create
PHP applications quickly, and effectively. It can be used to develop
most any PHP application. It also allow for the extension of the
built-in classes so that you can adapt the framework to meet your
specific needs.

